							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="terminal-line">
						<span class="prompt">nishant@dev:~$</span>
						<span class="command">cat experience.txt</span>
					</div>
					<div class="terminal-output">
						<div class="experience-section">
							<div class="company-header">
								<span class="company-name">
									<a href="https://kwike.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">kwike.in</a>
								</span>
								<span class="role">Founding Software Engineer</span>
							</div>
							<div class="achievements">
								<div class="achievement">
									<span class="achievement-icon">üöÄ</span>
									<span class="achievement-text">Built 3 production systems from scratch</span>
								</div>
								<div class="achievement">
									<span class="achievement-icon">üíº</span>
									<span class="achievement-text">CRM Platform</span>
								</div>
								<div class="achievement">
									<span class="achievement-icon">üõí</span>
									<span class="achievement-text">POS System</span>
								</div>
								<div class="achievement">
									<span class="achievement-icon">üåê</span>
									<span class="achievement-text">Main Website (<a href="https://kwike.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">kwike.in</a>)</span>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="focus-areas">
								<p><strong>Focus:</strong> Scalability ‚Ä¢ UX ‚Ä¢ Full-stack ownership</p>
								<p><strong>Pipeline:</strong> Architecture ‚Üí API ‚Üí Deployment ‚Üí Monitoring</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="terminal-line">
						<span class="prompt">nishant@dev:~$</span>
						<span class="command">cat philosophy.md</span>
					</div>
					<div class="terminal-output">
						<div class="philosophy">
							<p>
								<strong>Clean Code</strong> over clever code.<br>
