							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="terminal-line">
						<span class="prompt">nishant@dev:~$</span>
						<span class="command">./connect.sh</span>
					</div>
					<div class="terminal-output">
						<div class="connect-links">
							<a href={`mailto:${SITE_EMAIL}`} class="link">
								üìß Email Me
